Package org.bff.javampd.server

Class MPD

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bff.javampd.server.MPDServer
      • org.bff.javampd.server.MPD
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Server
    public class MPD
extends MPDServer
    MPD represents a connection to a MPD server. The commands are maintained in a properties file called mpd.properties.

    Uses the builder pattern for construction.

    Defaults are:

    server - localhost port - 6600 no timeout no password

    Author:
    Bill
